Package org.eclipse.keypop.calypso.crypto.asymmetric.certificate.spi

package org.eclipse.keypop.calypso.crypto.asymmetric.certificate.spi
SPIs dedicated to PKI certificates management to be implemented by a Calypso asymmetric crypto module.
